.TH PGADestroy 8 "05/01/95" " " "PGAPack"
.SH NAME
PGADestroy \- deallocate memory for this instance of PGAPack, if this context
initialized MPI, finalize MPI as well.
.SH INPUT PARAMETERS
.PD 0
.TP
ctx
- context variable
.PD 1
.SH OUTPUT PARAMETERS
.PD 0
.TP
none

.PD 1
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
#include "pgapack.h"
void  PGADestroy(ctx)
PGAContext *ctx
.fi
.SH LOCATION
system.c
.SH EXAMPLE
.nf
Example:
PGAContext *ctx;
:
PGADestroy(ctx);

.fi
